('oliveStrummer', 'OLIVE STRUMMER', 'TEMPLATE_NPC', 'LVL 2 NPC\r\n**12 HP**\r\nSPECIBUS: A trusty six string and a dream\r\n\r\nTALENTS: **+PLC**\r\nRAS: +1\r\nPLC: +4\r\nGRA: +2\r\nAPP: +0\r\nGRT: +0\r\nHUB: +2\r\nPSP: +2\r\nIMG: +1\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\nTROLLS WORLD TOUR (Country) [Musicreant]\r\nA FINE EAR [Musicreant]\r\nINSTRUMENT OF MURDER (Stringkind) [Musicreant]\r\nFRAYBATTLE [Musicreant]\r\n'),
('oliveSurvivalist', 'OLIVE SURVIVALIST ', 'CASTE_NPC', 'LVL 2 NPC\r\n**14 HP**\r\nSPECIBUS: A hunting spear\r\n\r\nTALENTS: **+HUB**\r\nRAS: +2\r\nPLC: +0\r\nGRA: +1\r\nAPP: +1\r\nGRT: +2\r\nHUB: +4\r\nPSP: +0\r\nIMG: +0\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\nWILD CAT (Spearkind) [Olive]\r\nVENATICS [Olive]\r\nBEAST MODE [Olive]\r\nCALL OF THE WILD [Olive]\r\n'),
('oliveTrader', 'OLIVE TRADER', 'CASTE_NPC', 'LVL 2 NPC\r\n**12 HP**\r\nSPECIBUS: A bag full o’ caegars, weaponized scale, or a back-up shotgun\r\n\r\nTALENTS: **+APP**\r\nRAS: +0\r\nPLC: +2\r\nGRA: +1\r\nAPP: +4\r\nGRT: +0\r\nHUB: +2\r\nPSP: +1\r\nIMG: +0\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\nMONEY CAT [Olive]\r\nHORNSWOGGLERY [Olive]\r\nLUCKY MERCHANT [Olive]\r\nCOOL CAT [Olive]\r\n'),
('orphanerDeepseaPredator', 'ORPHANER DEEPSEA PREDATOR', 'NPC_MONSTER', 'LVL 2 NPC\r\n**15 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **++GRT, +IMG**\r\nSTATS: +4 GRT, +3 IMG, +1 GRA, +2 ALL\r\nDeepsea Predators are among the most terrifying of Orphaners, raised in the darkest depths with a dangerous proximity to Gl\'bgolyb and recruited by the Orphaners as they rose to the surface. What they lack in finesse that their fellow hunters possess they make up for in the raw strength and power that ancient seadwellers once brought to bear to conquer the surface.\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\nDEEPSEA ENTITY\r\nWARP MUTATION\r\nCANONICAL SEADWELLER STRENGTH\r\nGLUB\'S CALL\r\n'),
('orphanerKaijuCombatant', 'ORPHANER KAIJU COMBATANT', 'NPC_MONSTER', 'LVL 3 NPC/ROBOT\r\n**20 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **++HUB, +GRA**\r\nSTATS: +4 HUB, +3 GRA, +3 HUB, +2 ALL\r\nPart Royal Guard. Part Orphaner. Alternia is a dangerous place from which some of the most feared beasts in the known galaxy originate. Obviously, trolls. But even trolls have to fight to remain at the top of the food chain. Titanic beasts prowl the galaxy, and it’s these mecha-piloting seadwellers who bag and tag them to both protect the public and to feed Gl\'bgolyb with a battle for the ages.\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\nMECHA MAYHEM\r\nONE ON ONE\r\nSKEWERSTRIKE\r\nTITANTIC FOE\r\nEJECTION SEAT'),
('orphanerLususRunner', 'ORPHANER LUSUS RUNNER', 'NPC_MONSTER', 'LVL 2 NPC\r\n**14 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+GRT, +HUB**\r\nSTATS: +4 GRT, +2 ALL\r\nThe everyday Orphaner works tirelessly to bring the ritually hunted lusus, wild monster and occasional oliveblood to feed Gl\'bgolyb lest She bring decimation to trollkind. Likewise, they are not afraid to bring the decimation themselves if interrupted in their duties with all their very, very lethal hunting equipment.\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\nHUNTRESS ON THE PROWL\r\nREST AT BONFIRE\r\nHUNTING EQUIPMENT\r\nCHARGED SHOT\r\n'),
('patrolDrone', 'PATROL DRONE', 'ROBOT_MONSTER', 'LVL 2 ROBOT\r\n**12 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+GRT, +HUB**\r\nSTATS: **+2 GRT, +2 APP, +2 HUB**\r\nThe expendable backup of the Alternian Army, Patrol Drones are not as ruthless or as dangerous as their bigger and better built robotic allies, but they are still able to give support to them in ways that their minigun carrying siblings can\'t. Namely, they can think enough to do things other than shoot gun.\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> MACHINE\r\n> SPECIALIZATION\r\n> PULVERIZE\r\n> ON CALL\r\n> HEAVY ARMOUR\r\n> ADDITIONAL AMMO STARTER PACK\r\n> SHOOT FIRST\r\n'),
('peer', 'PEER', 'ENTITY', 'LVL 1 ENTITY\r\n**6 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+PSP**\r\nSTATS: **+2 PSP**\r\nThis...shouldn’t be here. A lone eyeball, blinking and staring endlessly. Not like someone plucked it out, but more like a gif of an eye is just. There. Copy-pasted onto reality. S-stop looking at me!\r\n\r\nMOVES:\r\n> EYE SEE YOU\r\n> BLOODSHOT\r\n> CEASELESS WATCHER\r\n> BLINK OUT OF EXISTENCE \r\n> LASER POINTER'),
('pigeon', 'PIGEON', 'LUSUS', 'LVL 1 ANIMAL FROM REAL LIFE\r\n**4 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+RAS** \r\nSTATS: **+3 RAS, +2 PSP**\r\nIt’s a fucking pigeon. You make the Homestuck Tabletop Game next time. Fuck off, get off my back.\r\n\r\nMOVE: \r\n> COO\r\n> FLAP FLAP FLAP\r\n> NASTY SURPRISE\r\n> BIRD TYPE'),
('prizeberryPlant', 'PRIZEBERRY PLANT', 'PLANT', 'LVL 3 PLANT\r\n**20 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+GRA, +RAS**\r\nSTATS: **+3 GRA, +2 RAS, +2 GRT, -2 APP**\r\nYou think you learned about this thing in schoolfeeding! That is, if you\'re one of the castes that gets a decent education. The Prizeberry almost looks like a pitcher plant, with a big bulb surrounding a berry as big as your hand and plenty of vines covered in spitting pods. It grows in rainforests and jungles, preferring humidity. I think it\'s possible my father was one of these.\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> GOLDEN FRUIT\r\n> SPITTER\r\n> TRIPPING HAZARD\r\n> EXTREMELY FLAMMABLE'),
('psisucker', 'PSISUCKER', 'PLANT', 'LVL 2 PLANT\r\n**12 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **++APP, +IMG**\r\nSTATS: **+3 APP, +2 IMG**\r\nDeceptively small and almost pretty, the Psisucker plant is a pale blue flower that resembles a lily. It grows most often in dry climates and grassy plains, though occasionally it can be in deserts or wastelands. These flowers also have a nasty habit of popping up in urban centers and afflicting the occasional unlucky gold with Voidrot. Just like my aunt!\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> BATTERY DRAIN\r\n> POLLINATORS\r\n> INEDIBLE\r\n> PSI-SPLODE'),
('purrbeast', 'PURRBEAST', 'LUSUS', 'LVL 1 LUSUS\r\n**8 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+GRA, +GRT**\r\nSTATS: **+3 GRA, +2 GRT, +2 RAS**\r\nHeeheehee! APEX PREDATOR! Purrbeasts are feared for their quick reflexes, sharp claws, and even sharper fangs.\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> POUNCE\r\n> STEALTHY STALKER\r\n> TOP OF THE FOOD CHAIN\r\n> PREDATORY INSTINCT\r\n'),
('robofrog', 'ROBOFROG', 'ROBOT_MONSTER', 'LVL 0 ROBOT\r\n**2 HP**\r\nTALENTS: +PLC\r\nSTATS: +2 PLC, -1 APP\r\nJuenii Egredi, jade black sheep and CIS robotics extraordinaire, makes a ton of robots, many of them suited for surveillance and murder. Despite this, they’re best known for their cutest creation- robofrogs! Tens of thousands of robotic frogs now hop around the surface of Alternia, serving one important purpose- being your friend. :)\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> PURE HOPPINESS\r\n> JADE NEUTRALITY\r\n> TINY RIBBIT\r\n> SQUASHED FROG'),
('robopigeon', 'ROBO-PIGEON', 'ROBOT_MONSTER', 'LVL 2 ROBOT\r\n**12 HP**\r\nTALENTS: **+GRT, +PSP**\r\nSTATS: **+3 GRT, +2 PSP** \r\nMy god...they rebuilt it...they had the technology. This time, someone ELSE contributed to the Homestuck Tabletop Game! It’s a Robo-Pigeon, motherfucker!\r\n\r\nMOVES: \r\n> COO.MP4\r\n> VRRRR\r\n> DIVE BOMB\r\n> INFRARED\r\n> POORLY CONSTRUCTED'),
